CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 27 reads: "Dazzling Displays Exhibit Top Products at Fair...14. Bill Carter presenting Mrs. Bessie Mills with a set of four General puncture-sealing tires, one of the grand prizes...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Bill Carter presenting Bessie Mills with prize of four General Tires, standing in front demonstration kitchen with Jessie Vann and Louise Protho, in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
